      "title": "The Drop-the-Zero Rule",
      "content": "For any multiple of 10: nГ—10 Г· 10 = n. Just remove the trailing zero. 10Г·10=1, 20Г·10=2, 30Г·10=3, ... 90Г·10=9, 100Г·10=10. This works because 10 groups of n = 10n, so 10nГ·10 = n.",
